text: Minke Bisschops (born 2 September 2002) is a Dutch sprinter. Bisschops represents the Netherlands at international competitions. She competed at the 2022 World Athletics Championships in the 4 × 100 metres relay event. She also competed at the 2022 European Athletics Championships in München. ==References== Category:2002 births Category:Dutch sprinters Category:Living people
